TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Build your own base, then destroy all enemy units! Our intelligence indicates that you may be attacked. Luckily, we've built a radar near their base so you'll know when they are coming.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Press "i" to see how much wind/solar energy you get per collector/generator on the current map.
Hold down the shift key while giving multiple build/move/fight order to set up a queue.
